      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Parc%2C_New_York"
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "text": "The community was created after the Plattsburgh Air Force Base closed on September 25, 1995, to repurpose the 3,447‑acre industrial area.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
